rl=https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-51312008 |accessdate=2020-02-01 |date=2020-01-31 |work=BBC News 中文 |language=zh-Hans |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927205143/https://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-51312008 |dead-url=no }}</ref>7月30日由於疫情仍然嚴重，世衛宣布維持國際公衛緊急事件。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4748948 |title=全球疫情不止 世衛宣布維持國際公衛緊急事件 |accessdate=2020-08-02 |archive-date=2020-08-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824052735/https://udn.com/news/story/120944/4748948 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

此前，世界卫生组织曾在2020年1月22日至23日举行了关于冠状病毒爆发的突发事件委员会。<ref>{{Cite web |title=Travel ban goes into effect in Chinese city of Wuhan as authorities try to stop coronavirus spread |url=https://www.washingtonpost.com/ |accessdate=2020-01-31 |publisher=华盛顿邮报 |archive-date=2020-02-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200222154122/https://www.washingtonpost.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=WHO decision on nCoV emergency delayed as cases spike |url=http://www.cidrap.umn.edu/news-perspective/2020/01/who-decision-ncov-emergency-delayed-cases-spike |accessdate=2020-01-31 |publisher=Center for Infectious Disease Research and Policy |archive-date=2020-01-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200124063004/http://www.cidrap.umn.edu/news-perspective/2020/01/who-decision-ncov-emergency-delayed-cases-spike |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=世卫组织新型冠状病毒突发事件委员会将继续开会 |url=https://www.who.int/zh/dg/speeches/detail/who-director-general-s-statement-on-ihr-emergency-committee-on-novel-coronavirus |accessdate=2020-01-31 |publisher=世界卫生组织 |archive-date=2021-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210330141425/https://www.who.int/zh/director-general/speeches/detail/who-director-general-s-statement-on-ihr-emergency-committee-on-novel-coronavirus }}</ref>但是，由于缺乏必要的数据支持和其后续对世界的影响力规模而被认为宣布“国际关注的突发公共卫生事件”是为时过早。<ref>{{Cite web |title=WHO declines to declare China virus outbreak a global health emergency |url=https://www.statnews.com/2020/01/23/who-declines-to-declare-china-virus-outbreak-a-global-health-emergency/ |accessdate=2020-01-31 |publisher=STAT |author1=Andrew Joseph |archive-date=2020-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200123232041/https://www.statnews.com/2020/01/23/who-declines-to-declare-china-virus-outbreak-a-global-health-emergency/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |title=关于新型冠状病毒（2019-nCoV）疫情的《国际卫生条例（2005）》突发事件委员会会议的声明 |url=https://www.who.int/zh/news-room/detail/23-01-2020-statement-on-the-meeting-of-the-international-health-